project.name: JsonPullParser
project.description: Lightweight JSON library. at development, use the APT library. it generate a java source file on compile-time. at runtime, required library is a only core library(jsonpullparser-core). JsonPullParser can running on GAE/J, Android and normal Java enviroment.
